text: Back Door to Hell is a 1964 American Filipino World War II movie directed by Monte Hellman and stars Jack Nicholson, Jimmie Rodgers, Annabelle Huggins, John Hackett. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1964 war movies Category:American war movies Category:Filipino movies Category:World War II movies Category:Movies directed by Monte Hellman
title: Back Door to Hell
